WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:00.760
Well, welcome family.

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:04.770
Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:00:06.720 --> 00:00:08.263
We're going to just get right to praying.

00:00:08.263 --> 00:00:14.057
I've been really busy lately, and I'm so thankful for every single one of you.

00:00:14.057 --> 00:00:16.560
We're fine.

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:18.810
I had to take some days.

00:00:19.060 --> 00:00:26.347
The Lord said, 'You need more time focusing just with me.

00:00:26.347 --> 00:00:37.960
' And I've poured out and poured out, and I've got to the point where I feel dry and I said, 'I've got to get back underneath that waterfall.

00:00:37.960 --> 00:00:39.080
' It's personal.

00:00:48.079 --> 00:00:52.377
Just because I dump out with you all doesn't mean I don't keep vertical with him, and I want to make sure I'm hearing him in top shape.

00:00:52.377 --> 00:01:02.180
Keeping my relationship with him above all this other stuff; it doesn't matter to me if it all goes away tomorrow, I still have him.

00:01:02.180 --> 00:01:07.329
And that's what I want to make sure: that we're always good and that in my heart I'm seeking his face.

00:01:07.329 --> 00:01:16.000
There's so much ministry that pulls you every single day, and you can get distracted with it.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:26.091
Then you've got family, you've got kids you're raising, you've got a job you're working; there's things that are always pulling on you.

00:01:26.091 --> 00:01:34.009
But I have to make sure that I'm always staying sharp, especially when you're talking to as many people as we do.

00:01:34.009 --> 00:01:36.379
And so I take the time.

00:01:36.379 --> 00:01:39.611
After the tornado, I was frustrated with that.

00:01:39.611 --> 00:01:44.731
We have power and authority over storms, you know, and God has given us that.

00:01:55.296 --> 00:01:55.552
As he is, so are we in this world.

00:01:57.088 --> 00:02:05.440
And as we see tornadoes come and they're wreaking havoc and doing all that they're doing and everybody's afraid, I warned you all.

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:27.120
I said there are storms coming.

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:29.289
It's not just in the natural storms, but spiritual storms.

00:02:30.353 --> 00:02:35.771
And there's a lot of you that are still asleep and you say, 'Well, Brandon, you know what?

00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:48.160
Whenever I see a storm and it's a tornado right in front of me, well, I'm just going to be bold and just go out there like David and say, "Who is this uncircumcised Philistine that defies the armies of God?

00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:50.137
"' No, this tornado or whatever.

00:02:50.137 --> 00:03:04.239
Or, you know, when the plague comes again that I've told you countless times the Lord has warned me about, we must take authority and start to activate that inside of you.

00:03:04.239 --> 00:03:11.930
Psalm 91, Psalm 23, getting it down inside of your heart because of the storm that I've seen over and over.

00:03:13.780 --> 00:03:19.440
Financial storms, financial crisis, major shakings to awaken.

00:03:19.440 --> 00:03:30.879
And the only way you're going to weather the storm is by knowing who you are in Christ, by having a foundation of the word of God down inside of yourself, staying vertical.

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:36.329
If I'm not here and YouTube was to go away, where will you be?

00:03:36.329 --> 00:03:45.270
If these other people—there's a lot of you that are baby Christians—but you must learn and have the meat of the word down inside of you.

00:03:45.270 --> 00:03:48.137
You've got to get that backbone like a crowbar.

00:03:48.137 --> 00:03:49.733
Who are you listening to?

00:03:49.733 --> 00:03:51.209
Who's pouring into your life?

00:03:51.209 --> 00:03:54.580
I like to listen to Reinhard Bonnke a lot.

00:03:54.580 --> 00:03:56.377
Reinhard Bonnke is one of my favorites.

00:03:56.377 --> 00:04:08.159
After he prayed for me and laid hands on me that day I told you all, when I was a young man and I got an impartation that day, it changed my life forever.

00:04:08.159 --> 00:04:14.151
And when Reinhard Bonnke prayed for me, he said, 'I put a double portion of the anointing that's on my life on you.

00:04:14.151 --> 00:04:18.933
' And he laid hands on me and the fire of God—I'm talking a lightning bolt—came out of heaven.

00:04:19.280 --> 00:04:20.582
It felt this way.

00:04:20.582 --> 00:04:21.629
It shook me.

00:04:21.629 --> 00:04:25.920
I was like a sack of potatoes on the ground when that happened.

00:04:25.920 --> 00:04:29.769
It changed me when I got up off the floor.

00:04:29.769 --> 00:04:33.680
And I'm not giving any glory to Reinhard Bonnke.

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:36.728
Reinhard Bonnke was just a man that was yielded to Jesus.

00:04:37.104 --> 00:04:42.880
But I always respect my elders and I respect the anointing.

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:48.925
And there was impartation that day; there was something that happened, there was an exchange.

00:04:48.925 --> 00:04:59.510
And ever since then, between him and Ralph Wilkerson, there has been a stirring on the inside of me, a fire shut up in my bones that you just can't control.

00:04:59.940 --> 00:05:01.280
And do you have that?

00:05:01.280 --> 00:05:04.160
Do you have to have an impartation from somebody to get that?

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:04.338
No.

00:05:04.338 --> 00:05:07.863
You can have it right in the middle of your house right now where you're watching.

00:05:07.863 --> 00:05:15.051
But you've got to get yourself in the river in prayer and worship and seeking him daily.

00:05:15.051 --> 00:05:18.148
Not just on Sundays and whenever they have something at the church.

00:05:18.148 --> 00:05:21.691
You've got to have a personal relationship with Jesus where you're going vertical.

00:05:21.691 --> 00:05:24.320
I told you there's a storm coming.

00:05:24.320 --> 00:05:29.199
I told you there's a shaking to awaken coming to our nation.

00:05:29.199 --> 00:05:31.600
We must pray for President Trump.

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:47.680
As you can see, I told you this is not just the one opportunity that I've seen; there's much more that we have to pray for our president to make it across the finish line of what God has called him to do.

00:05:47.680 --> 00:05:52.000
The enemy would try to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:05:52.000 --> 00:05:52.560
Right?

00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:59.520
We know what the devil's mode of operation, his whole plan is.

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:03.384
So we've got to come against it by the blood of the Lamb.

00:06:03.384 --> 00:06:04.766
We've got to plead the blood.

00:06:04.766 --> 00:06:06.457
You've got to take communion daily.

00:06:06.457 --> 00:06:10.479
You've got to seek his face daily.

00:06:10.479 --> 00:06:15.840
We must work while it is still light, for night is coming.

00:06:15.840 --> 00:06:28.720
It's time for us to get an enthusiasm inside of us, a stirring on the inside of us knowing that the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ is at hand.

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:30.670
The church must wake up.

00:06:30.670 --> 00:06:37.248
It's not just about filling pews or chairs at the church, having full auditoriums.

00:06:37.248 --> 00:06:49.840
It's about telling people that it's time to repent and it's time to fall down on our knees before a holy God and get right with him because there's many of you that are about to be left.

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:56.579
It's time to come to church with a heart of worship and thanksgiving for what he's already done in your life.

00:06:56.579 --> 00:07:00.720
But get ready, for he is about to do something even greater.

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:08.160
The greatest outpouring of the Spirit of God is about to hit this earth like we've never seen before.

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:13.360
What we have seen in the past is nothing compared to what we're about to see.

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:30.720
And there's many of you that are so lackadaisical in your relationship with the Lord and you're so lukewarm and you don't even realize that the water is getting hot all around you and the pot is beginning to boil and you're in it.

00:07:30.720 --> 00:07:31.164
We see it.

00:07:32.053 --> 00:07:43.546
And I have such an urgency inside of me every single time I do these broadcasts to warn you that the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ is at hand.

00:07:43.546 --> 00:07:53.909
I shout it from the mountaintops and I shout it in the valleys: Jesus Christ is coming.

00:07:53.919 --> 00:07:57.360
But what are we waiting for?

00:07:57.360 --> 00:08:02.240
He has long patience for the harvest, his fruit.

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:05.640
And right now, he said, 'Brandon, I'm not out of patience.

00:08:05.640 --> 00:08:07.440
I'm out of time.

00:08:07.440 --> 00:08:10.582
This dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

00:08:10.582 --> 00:08:14.320
' He's had long patience for thousands of years now.

00:08:14.320 --> 00:08:17.450
But this dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

00:08:17.450 --> 00:08:29.430
The Lord Jesus Christ is coming for his church, but he's coming back for a bride that's without spot or wrinkle, that is sold out to him and not sold out to the world.

00:08:29.440 --> 00:08:35.413
So I want to tell you again and again, you must get your heart right before him.

00:08:35.413 --> 00:08:38.880
It's time to repent.

00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:42.240
Now I know there's a lot of you that want to know what's going on in the news.

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:50.617
But the biggest headline I can tell you that's going on in the news is the signs of the times of the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ are all around you.

00:08:50.617 --> 00:08:52.709
Are you looking?

00:08:52.709 --> 00:08:55.976
Are you watching the alarm bells?

00:08:57.544 --> 00:09:00.387
The sun is setting on this dispensation.

00:09:00.387 --> 00:09:03.360
I'm telling you, I know beyond a shadow of a doubt.

00:09:03.360 --> 00:09:06.342
I had a Holy Ghost dream last night again.

00:09:06.342 --> 00:09:09.639
The Lord visited me again last night in my dreams, and he visits me.

00:09:09.639 --> 00:09:10.1000
Those are for me.

00:09:10.1000 --> 00:09:15.370
The visions are what I tell you, but I don't tell you about my dreams.

00:09:15.370 --> 00:09:25.371
The Lord visits me and talks to me about my own personal life a lot and talks to me and my wife, and there's an urgency.

00:09:25.371 --> 00:09:30.800
He says there are some things that are about to happen.

00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:32.994
I've warned you about the economy.

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:35.554
When was the last time we were together?

00:09:45.093 --> 00:09:45.476
What did the Lord tell us?

00:09:45.476 --> 00:09:49.693
We saw so much, all to his glory.

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:57.291
I want to say everything we see or what we do on this channel is just all for his glory.

00:09:57.291 --> 00:09:59.530
This isn't about Brandon.

00:09:59.530 --> 00:10:02.399
This isn't a Brandon show.

00:10:02.399 --> 00:10:09.849
This I believe with all my heart God's put it on us for this generation to be watchmen and watchwomen?

00:10:14.662 --> 00:10:16.376
To tell you what the Lord gives us in prayer so that we can pray and change things.

00:10:16.376 --> 00:10:19.297
Some of it we can't.

00:10:19.297 --> 00:10:27.819
But my main job is always to come on here and always give God glory in everything I say in word and in deed.

00:10:27.819 --> 00:10:29.497
We give all to the glory of God.

00:10:33.051 --> 00:10:35.159
Can I miss it?

00:10:35.159 --> 00:10:38.399
Yeah, we can miss it.

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:52.674
We're human.

00:10:52.674 --> 00:11:03.453
We're all saved by grace and we're all trying our best to get out to the other side and hear him say, "Well done, thy good and faithful servant.

00:11:03.453 --> 00:11:05.519
Enter into my rest.

00:11:07.920 --> 00:11:08.120
" And that's what I'm after.

00:11:08.120 --> 00:11:09.859
But can Brandon Biggs miss it?

00:11:09.859 --> 00:11:12.240
Yes, I can miss it.

00:11:20.730 --> 00:11:20.920
And anybody that tells you they've never missed it is usually either a liar or something else.

00:11:20.920 --> 00:11:29.760
I'm just telling you, everybody has a chance that we all are working out our salvation with fear and trembling and we're going from glory to glory.

00:11:29.760 --> 00:11:31.703
Every one of us.

00:11:31.703 --> 00:11:44.560
But I want to tell you my main mission every single time I come on here is to throw out the net and see how many fish I can bring in.

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:53.973
I told you what was coming by the spirit and the leading of the Holy Spirit.

00:12:06.108 --> 00:12:06.305
I believe with what he showed us last time when we were here.

00:12:06.501 --> 00:12:08.205
I saw President Trump at the desk.

00:12:14.206 --> 00:12:19.840
I saw a dove with an olive branch in its beak and he was flapping his wings over him and I saw church bells ringing around his desk and the Lord said, "Pray for him.

00:12:19.840 --> 00:12:21.639
" Then we prayed for John Kilpatrick.

00:12:21.639 --> 00:12:24.079
We prayed for Perry Stone.

00:12:24.879 --> 00:12:33.851
The Lord showed me praying over their health, praying over them—these two men—and then Jentezen Franklin and my friend Billy Burke and these others.

00:12:37.880 --> 00:12:39.440
The Lord said, "I have much more for them to do.

00:12:56.926 --> 00:12:57.177
Pray for their health that they would be restored with the glory to be restored like Moses, that his eyes did not grow dim.

00:12:58.205 --> 00:13:04.123
" And I saw a renewing like the eagles, that their flesh would not fade with the glory.

00:13:04.123 --> 00:13:05.546
The glory kept them.

00:13:05.546 --> 00:13:06.970
The glory kept Moses.

00:13:06.970 --> 00:13:12.360
The glory will keep these men.

00:13:13.440 --> 00:13:16.453
And I saw to pray for them more.

00:13:16.453 --> 00:13:19.063
So we prayed for them last broadcast.

00:13:19.063 --> 00:13:23.130
Then we prayed for President Trump and the Lord said, "Pray for a protection around him.

00:13:36.453 --> 00:13:36.880
" And I saw that in the days ahead we saw by the spirit of the Lord that the Lord warned us that there would be three Senate seats and it would flip blue.

00:13:38.560 --> 00:13:45.596
The Lord said, "You see this?

00:13:58.610 --> 00:13:58.920
It's increasing.

00:14:10.869 --> 00:14:11.099
" And I saw it went from one—they would have it by one—to having it by three.

00:14:13.400 --> 00:14:25.017
And he said, "If you don't start praying now, they will win the House and the Senate and your president is in jeopardy even by impeachment.

00:14:25.017 --> 00:14:26.594
" 25th Amendment.

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:32.480
The 25th Amendment.

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:44.752
There's so many things that the Lord has brought to us to pray over concerning President Trump and we will continue to do so.

00:14:54.389 --> 00:14:54.639
But the main things I have on my heart right now is your life and your heart.

00:14:54.639 --> 00:14:58.070
Where are you with Jesus?

00:14:58.070 --> 00:15:00.267
Do you know him?

00:15:03.475 --> 00:15:03.750
And more importantly, does he know you?

00:15:03.750 --> 00:15:13.462
I'm not talking about your grandma's religion that she used to talk to you about as a little boy.

00:15:13.462 --> 00:15:22.570
You say, "Well, yeah, you know, grandma used to talk about Jesus all the time.

00:15:22.570 --> 00:15:26.770
" I'm talking about a personal relationship with the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:15:26.770 --> 00:15:28.869
Do you know him?

00:15:28.869 --> 00:15:34.720
If you were to die tonight, where would you spend eternity?

00:15:48.080 --> 00:15:48.240
There is a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

00:15:48.240 --> 00:15:53.510
We've heard it all the time, especially if you've been in the church a long time.

00:15:55.490 --> 00:15:55.800
But this is a true statement.

00:16:00.919 --> 00:16:01.209
The Lord said to go over some of the things I saw when I went to tribulation tonight.

00:16:01.209 --> 00:16:05.920
So, I am being obedient to what he told me to do real quick.

00:16:05.920 --> 00:16:07.220
So, bear with me.

00:16:07.220 --> 00:16:11.634
It's 15 minutes, but I'm going to go over this really quick.

00:16:29.720 --> 00:16:30.560
I saw the day that I was on July 6th, 2014, I was taken out of my body and the Lord Jesus Christ came in my room and he took me to tribulation.

00:16:30.560 --> 00:16:36.468
It was one of the most life-changing experiences I've ever had.

00:16:36.468 --> 00:16:39.680
It shook me like I can't even tell you.

00:16:41.813 --> 00:16:47.519
I went from year to year with him as we would travel into the years of tribulation.

00:16:55.250 --> 00:16:55.600
I saw the day it happens.

00:17:14.853 --> 00:17:18.995
I saw what happens when the rapture takes place.

00:17:25.956 --> 00:17:26.418
And the Lord allowed me to see it happened at night in America.

00:17:32.790 --> 00:17:33.140
It was not night in other parts of the world, of course, but it was night in America.

00:17:41.299 --> 00:17:41.559
I saw lightning shooting all over the sky.

00:17:41.559 --> 00:17:42.600
Everything was alive.

00:17:44.149 --> 00:17:46.720
The lightning was just bolting and there was no thunder.

00:18:06.630 --> 00:18:06.880
It was just a light show.

00:18:10.880 --> 00:18:11.840
And I remember the lady screaming, "The aliens came and got them!

00:18:12.840 --> 00:18:13.173
The aliens!

00:18:13.173 --> 00:18:18.103
" That's what they...

00:18:34.680 --> 00:18:34.940
they were deceived.

00:18:36.240 --> 00:18:37.110
They didn't know where everybody disappeared.

00:18:37.110 --> 00:18:41.691
Everybody from the children that were age 15 and younger were all gone.

00:18:41.691 --> 00:18:47.730
So their mothers were all frantically looking for their children.

00:18:47.730 --> 00:18:57.591
They were screaming through the streets and they were looking and calling out their names and they were in panic looking for the kids that were gone.

00:18:57.591 --> 00:19:03.565
All the mothers were running up and down the street screaming for their children and they were all raptured.

00:19:03.565 --> 00:19:06.580
Now, there's some of you that don't believe in the rapture.

00:19:06.580 --> 00:19:07.120
That's fine.

00:19:07.120 --> 00:19:14.137
If you don't want to hear this, click out and go away.

00:19:14.137 --> 00:19:24.584
But I'm telling you, for those that are here and you want to know what's coming, I'm going to tell you.

00:19:32.559 --> 00:19:32.811
I believe in the rapture of the church.

00:19:44.720 --> 00:19:45.013
I believe in what I experienced and when I went to tribulation, I believe that God is not a wife beater.

00:19:45.013 --> 00:19:47.067
We're not appointed unto wrath.

00:19:50.057 --> 00:19:50.514
And we are not going to go through the tribulation.

00:19:50.514 --> 00:20:04.559
If you're a believing believer and you have your lamp full of oil—there were ten virgins: five had their lamps full and five didn't—which one are you?

00:20:13.387 --> 00:20:21.039
And I saw believers that didn't have their lamps full of oil and they were not expecting the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:20:25.210 --> 00:20:25.520
And they were running frantically yelling.

00:20:25.520 --> 00:20:39.660
And I saw one lady that I knew and she was flipping off the Lord, giving the finger to the Lord, yelling at him because she didn't go.

00:20:39.660 --> 00:20:42.480
She knew.

00:20:42.480 --> 00:20:48.538
They knew what happened.

00:21:02.036 --> 00:21:11.062
And I saw pastors that were preaching a compromising word that didn't have a backbone like a crowbar telling the people that they needed to repent and turn from their wicked ways, that they believed and they preached a solid lukewarm grace gospel that everything's about grace, brother.

00:21:11.062 --> 00:21:14.159
And I believe we're all saved by grace.

00:21:17.360 --> 00:21:23.119
But there is a place where we don't act like we used to.

00:21:36.026 --> 00:21:36.284
The very sins we repented of, we went back to, and you live in there.

00:21:44.651 --> 00:21:44.914
The things that you say, "I was once lost and now I'm found.

00:21:44.914 --> 00:21:47.519
" You say, "I'm back living in it.

00:21:47.519 --> 00:21:57.200
" And you say, "Well, I'm still saved," but I'm going to tell you, you're mistaken.

00:21:57.200 --> 00:22:06.000
When I saw the people and they were running all over the place screaming and they were so upset because there was no peace.

00:22:12.800 --> 00:22:13.760
The peace that passes all understanding abides in every believer.

00:22:13.760 --> 00:22:26.180
You don't even realize that you wake up every single day and the Holy Spirit's leading you for the first time...

00:22:29.500 --> 00:22:32.080
that prayer covering that was there—and people take it for granted.

00:22:32.080 --> 00:22:44.400
Even the world wakes up every single day and there's a prayer covering that the church brings that is no longer here.

00:22:48.640 --> 00:22:49.040
And they all act crazy.

00:22:49.040 --> 00:22:50.800
They're burning buildings.

00:22:50.800 --> 00:22:52.419
They're burning cars.

00:22:52.419 --> 00:22:53.200
They're murdering.

00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:53.980
They're raping.

00:22:53.980 --> 00:22:55.340
They're pillaging.

00:23:05.920 --> 00:23:06.320
It was awful.

00:23:06.320 --> 00:23:13.343
It looked like Sodom and Gomorrah, what I would picture it to be.

00:23:13.343 --> 00:23:14.160
All nuts.

00:23:14.160 --> 00:23:16.720
They had no balance at all.

00:23:18.640 --> 00:23:23.493
I saw fires and smoke, burning cars all across the city as the Lord said, "Look.

00:23:35.942 --> 00:23:36.308
" And he never spoke anything.

00:23:36.308 --> 00:23:41.850
He just touched my hand and I perceived everything he was saying.

00:23:41.850 --> 00:23:44.120
He never had to speak anything.

00:24:22.983 --> 00:24:23.684
I just could hear him.

00:24:33.039 --> 00:24:35.600
And I went through and I could see the lady screaming because I walked up to her because she could see me.

00:24:35.600 --> 00:24:48.070
That was the only time that somebody could see me in tribulation.

00:25:03.902 --> 00:25:04.364
I walked up to her and I said, "What happened?

00:25:04.364 --> 00:25:09.520
" And she goes, "Don't you know the Christians are all gone?

00:25:09.520 --> 00:25:12.000
Don't you know they're all gone?

00:25:16.100 --> 00:25:16.320
The Christians are all gone.

00:25:16.320 --> 00:25:18.194
" She was screaming.

00:25:34.035 --> 00:25:34.417
I saw the Antichrist come on the scene.

